reviews.review_text:
Finally Complete! Great sound, strong performance.
today for the first time I noticed the "conversation" on stage at the end of Truckin' around the 11 minute mark where Jerry wants to play "Here Comes Sunshine" but eventually gets overruled and they end up on Playin!
Peace, Bob
